Political Solution to Kosovo Issue Possible : Official
TIRANA , December 23 ( Xinhua ) -- Political solution to the Kosovo issue is still possible despite objective difficulties and complex regional situation , NATO commander for Europe General Wesley Clark said Wednesday .
Warning against escalating violence in the turbulent Serb province after meeting with Macedonian Prime Minister Ljubco Georgievski in the capital city of Skopje , he said , " We are watching the situation very closely and we are seeing increasing Serb military and police activities . "
He noted that these activities do not conform to the promises of the Yugoslav government and have caused great concern in the international community .
He urged all parties , including the Kosovo Albanians , to refrain from violence .
Clark arrived in Skopje for a visit Tuesday following his trip to Belgrade on Monday .
